          <p>The first stage of your training is a 90-day session that will be a kick-start to your learning experience and is designed to build foundational business skills and enhance your technical elevator acumen. The initial part of this stage will be an introduction and orientation to the company as a whole. You will learn about our Three Absolutes: Safety, Ethics and Controls and participate in comprehensive training in these areas. You will be introduced to elevators through learning modules as well as participate in firsthand field experiences to see elevators being installed, repaired, and maintained.</p>

