          <img alt="" class="responsive-img img-float left" src="<?php echo e(asset('/img/training/03.jpg')); ?>"><h5>Learning &amp; Observation</h5><p>During the Learning and Observation stage, you will complete 12 modules that can be accessed through the regional SharePoint site. Each module includes reading materials, field experience and a knowledge check. You will be required to complete several tasks such as, reading on-line materials, connecting with your colleagues to observe them on the job, conducting research, and preparing sales presentations.</p>

          <p>At the end of 12 weeks, you will take a comprehensive quiz, which will assess your professional development needs related to your knowledge of OTIS products and services learned during this stage of training. In addition, throughout the 12 weeks, you will be expected to prepare several presentations on concepts learned through field experience.</p>
